Mechel Seeks Raspadskaya for Less Than Holders Want, RIA Says

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-03-28T18:48:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/mechel-seeks-raspadskaya-for-less-than-holders-want-ria-says.html
OAO  Mechel (MTLR) ,  Russia ’s largest miner,
is seeking to buy OAO Raspadskaya at a price almost three times
lower than what the coal company’s shareholders are looking for,
RIA Novosti reported, citing unidentified sources.  Mechel is prepared to pay no more than $2.3 billion, RIA
reported. Raspadskaya’s shareholders put the company’s value at
$6 billion, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran at 
